      "description": "You can specify different settings for where you'd like this document to be generated. For example, we can use `OpenApiDocumentsDirectory` to save the OpenAPI spec into the project directory instead of `obj/`. \r\n\r\nWe can also use `OpenApiGenerateDocumentsOptions` to specify the file name. Normally, it's the name of the project. However, here we change it to `openapi-spec`.\r\n\r\nThere's a few more settings available, which you can find in the docs."
    },
