      "description": "We might want to change the way OpenAPI files are generated. There's quite a lot of options available in the `AddOpenApi` overloads!\r\n\r\nWe're not going through all of them. Some more are covered in the docs. I want to focus on the transformers.\r\n\r\nFirst, let's look at the OpenAPI version. We can switch to OpenAPI 3.0, 3.1 or 2."
